B.IF={titleApp:0,hdrSettings:1,hdrHelp:2,pptHelp:3,pptDuration:4,btnClose:5,btnSettingsTheme:6,btnSettingsMode:7,"btnSettingsTheme-C0":8,"btnSettingsTheme-C1":9,"btnSettingsTheme-C2":10,"btnSettingsTheme-C3":11,"btnSettingsTheme-C4":12,"btnSettingsTheme-C5":13,"btnSettingsMode-M0":14,"btnSettingsMode-M1":15,"btnSettingsMode-M2":16,txtHelp:17,"determination-0":18,"determination-1":19,"determination-2":20,"determination-3":21,"determination-4":22}
B.HV=new A.bn(B.IF,["Ephemeral Voice","Settings","Help","Help","Duration: ${0} seconds","Close","Color Theme: ${0}","Theme Mode: ${0}","Red","Orange","Yellow","Green","Blue","Purple","System","Light","Dark","## About\n\nThis app lets you record and play back audio without saving files to your computer. It is designed for temporary use cases, such as voice or music training, where you want to hear yourself but don't need to keep the recording. If you need to save or edit your recordings, this app is not for you.\n\nWhether you are perfecting a cartoon voice, rehearsing for a play, or simply working to feel more comfortable in your own voice, listening to yourself can be difficult. Trust me, I get it. For some people, this rings especially true. Don't give up. If you keep working at it, even just a little every day, you can do it. Don't be afraid to experiment and try new, even silly, things. Be proud of your progress and the effort you put in.\n\n## User Guide\n\nThe app interface is simple, featuring four control buttons and three operating modes. The first three buttons represent the current mode: Recording, Stopped, and Playback. The active mode is indicated by the highlighted button.\n\n- **To Record**: Press the microphone button (you will need to grant microphone access). The recording duration will count up. Note that new recordings will overwrite any previous ones.\n- **To Play**: Press the play button. A progress bar across the screen shows your position in the recording.\n- **To Stop**: Press the stop button. If you stop during playback, the position will reset to the start.\n- **Loop Mode**: The far-right button toggles between looping the recording and playing it just once. Press it to switch modes.\n\n## Privacy Policy\n\nNo data is collected or saved externally. That's it. No data is collected, and no data will be collected.\n","Apparently this popup is called a snackbar, making this message a snack? Knowing this fills you with determination (and maybe slightly hungry)!","You remember a mountain path with a red strawberry waiting for you at the top. Thinking of the strawberry fills you with determination!","Imagine the Beast in you is like a truck, revving its engine, ready for a race. Feeling this energy fills you with determination!","As the shining sun sets, the sky is filled with a golden glow. Knowing the sun will rise up again tomorrow fills you with determination!","Shattered glass, fused together leaving scars behind. As the sun shines through the stained class window and you see its beauty, you are filled with determination!"],t.li)
